history.content: Looking for a club that bridges the fields of Data Science and Social Good? DataGood @ Berkeley is a student-run organization dedicated to tackling social issues ranging from public health to wildfires with data science. Our external team collaborates alongside industry partners in making a direct impact to the social sector. Our internal team runs project teams applying data science and machine learning to health, education, sustainability, racial equity, and more. Join our recruitment discord for more details: https://discord.gg/VuNX2rC2GV (or click the link in our bio) and you can find our app at datagood.berkeley.edu/join!
history.subject: Join DataGood at Berkeley!
